I've added a CLS patch to my install of DSD, if anyone else wants to use it, here it is.

    @PART[DSD1]:HAS[!MODULE[ModuleConnectedLivingSpace]] {    MODULE	{		name = ModuleConnectedLivingSpace		passable = true	}}@PART[DSD2]:HAS[!MODULE[ModuleConnectedLivingSpace]] {    MODULE	{		name = ModuleConnectedLivingSpace		passable = true	}}

I play with CLS and Ship Manifest, so having this entry makes my life alot easier.
